// Example of using the FPP plugin.

Plugin FPP

Time 4/4
MSet pat1
E |--------|
B |--7---7-|
G |-7-7-7-7|
D |--7---7-|
A |--------|
E |9---8---|
MSetEnd
Plectrum @fpp pp1, pat1, Debug=0

// Adjust chords so they have bass on 6th string
Begin Plectrum Shape
    Em     0 2 2 0 0 0
    Am     5 0 2 2 1 0
    B7     7 2 1 2 0 2
End

// Init Plectrum track (once),
$PPSetup

// Set a pattern
$PP1   Em
       Am
       B7
       Em
